NonLinearModelScorer

Source: R/model_scoring.R
NonLinearModelScorer.Rd

An R6 class to score non-linear regression models on new data and visualize the results.

Public fields

fit_results

A list of fitted model objects.

scored_data

A list of data.tables containing scored data.

score_plots

A list of plots visualizing scored data.

Method score_new_data()

Usage

NonLinearModelScorer$score_new_data(new_data, x_col)

Arguments

new_data

A data.table containing the new data to score.

x_col

Returns
